entries.femaleVariant: Let's talk.
Fuck you want, huh? Answer when I ask you a fuckin' question!
Heard you have scandium rods. My client needs 'em.
Oh yeah? What about me? I don't need 'em?
You won't get anything fixed in that state.
My client gave me the green light to end you.
Won't get anything fixed in that state. You look like you just snorted a mountain of syn-blow.
Oh, you wanna know, huh? The gist – he couldn't give a shit about you. I put a bullet in your head right now, he won't even blink.
Yeah? Then try me! Fuckin' try me!
You're Gallo, right? Listen, I've got--
Calm down. Let's just talk.
Oh, I'm calm. I'm real fuckin' calm. Way fuckin' calmer than you are!
Umm... OK...
You're hidin' somethin', I know it. What're you not tellin' me, huh? Fuckin' rip it outta ya!
This whole goddamn building's goin' to shit – all of it! Pipes, power... Every other day the elevator jams. That motherfuckin' elevator!
How the fuck am I s'posed to fix it if I ain't got no rods, eh? Your client even consider that? The fuck he say to you?!
I'll tell you how to fix them without rods.
This elevator – is it wired or pumped?
What? Well... motor's electric. With a speed reducer.
Sounds like a non-conductive hitch. Insulation in the cables must've worn out and short-circ'd. Open-and-shut case.
The fuck...? You from maintenance or something?
Nope, third party sent me. He really wants those rods, Gallo, and here's the thing... You'll manage without 'em.
And what if I did? You got a problem with that?
Keep talking like that.
Nope, none at all.
Keep runnin' your mouth, and I'll have you chokin' on pieces of your own jaw.
Go ahead, try it, you ugly bitch! Come on!
entries.maleVariant: Go ahead, try it, you ugly fuck! Come on!

entries.femaleVariant: Nope, none at all. But my client does. That's why you an' me are talkin'.
Tell your "client" to go fuck himself! Ya hear me?!
I'll pass it along. But lemme fill ya in on one little detail. He never forgets – never forgives. Keep sendin' peeps 'til he gets what wants.
So let's not make this any harder than it has to be. Give back the rods, and I'll be on my way.
Over there, take 'em. And then fuck off! Heads 'bout to explode...
'Ey, hands off, you dirty-ass punk!
You afraid of the dark, huh? 'Cause you fucking should be!
Nothin', actually. Was just leavin'.
You have scandium rods, right?
Nothing. Just leaving.
Then fuckin' pivot and haul ass outta here! You ever come back, I spill your fucking guts!
Hey, relax.
